            <title>2.0.3</title>
            <pubDate>Sun, 03 May 2026 20:44:00 +0900</pubDate>
            <link>https://github.com/Saqoosha/Canopy</link>
            <sparkle:version>41</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>2.0.3</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>15.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <sparkle:hardwareRequirements>arm64</sparkle:hardwareRequirements>
            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[### Bug Fixes
- Cloud session teleport now prompts you to pick a local clone with a folder picker when no matching recent directory is found (or when multiple match). Previously failed silently with a toast.
- Fixed branch checkout always reporting failure after a successful teleport. The "Resumed locally but couldn't switch to branch ..." toast no longer appears when checkout actually succeeded.
]]></description>
